Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Frida fails to attach to application

Verify device is connected: adb devices
Check Frida server is running on device: adb shell ps | grep frida
Restart Frida server: adb shell killall frida-server && adb shell /data/local/tmp/frida-server &
Issue: Hooks not triggering

Verify correct class and method names using frida-trace
Check if app uses custom permission checking methods
Ensure Java.perform() wrapper is used correctly
Issue: Application crashes after hooking

Check return types match original method signatures
Verify all parameters are handled correctly
Use try-catch blocks around hook implementations
Issue: Python script cannot find device

Confirm USB debugging is enabled
Check ADB recognizes device: adb devices
Try specifying device ID explicitly in script
